PREPARED STATEMENT OF HON. JOHN THUNE, U.S. SENATOR FROM SOUTH DAKOTA 
I would like to thank Senator Dorgan for convening this hearing. I would also like 
to  thank  our  witnesses  for  taking  time  out  of  their  schedules  to  testify  before  our 
committee today. 

